ğŸ”¹ 1. Updating Package Index (Debian/Ubuntu)

Before installing anything, always refresh the list of available packages:

sudo apt update

This doesnâ€™t install updates â€” it just fetches the latest package info from repositories.

ğŸ”¹ 2. Installing Packages

On Debian/Ubuntu:

sudo apt install nginx


On CentOS/RedHat:

